パッケージ org.wcardinal.controller.annotation

Annotation Interface DisplayNameMessage

@Documented @Target({TYPE,FIELD}) @Retention(RUNTIME) public @interface DisplayNameMessage
Represents display name settings.

  • 任意要素の概要

    任意要素
    修飾子とタイプ
    任意要素
    説明
    String
    value
    Returns the message ID of the display name.

  • 要素の詳細

    • value

      String value
      Returns the message ID of the display name. If the returned display name is empty, ControllerContext.getName() is used instead.
      戻り値:
      display name
